<![CDATA[<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []" style=""><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Dear&nbsp;</span>{!leaseworks__Technical_Project__c.Account_Holder__c}</font></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">This is an automated notification to inform you that you have been assigned as Project Owner(Account Owner) to the project. Please see below for some information on this project, along with a direct link to it.</p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Project Name:&nbsp;<a href="{!leaseworks__Technical_Project__c.Link}">{!leaseworks__Technical_Project__c.Name}</a></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Project Type: {!leaseworks__Technical_Project__c.leaseworks__Project_Type__c}</p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Associated Assembly:&nbsp;<a href="https://leaseworks-carlyle.lightning.force.com/lightning/r/leaseworks__Constituent_Assembly__c/{!leaseworks__Technical_Project__c.Assembly_localId__c}/view">{!leaseworks__Technical_Project__c.Assembly_local__c}</a></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Project Description: {!leaseworks__Technical_Project__c.leaseworks__Project_Description__c}</p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Thanks</p>]]></td>
</tr>
